title: The Stone Roses - The Stone Roses [1989 US edition]
description:
The Stone Roses is the debut eponymous album by Madchester band from Manchester The Stone Roses. It is regarded as one of the all time best albums of british music by critics. The album was produced by John Leckie who previously worked with Pink Floyd on "Meddle".
